1. *Radimo* u udruženju već nekoliko godina. (We have been working in the association for several years.)

2. *Radimo* na projektu zajedno. (We are working on the project together.)

3. Ona je prethodne nedelje *radila* na projektu. (She was working on the project the previous week.)

4. Oni će *raditi* ovih dana na projektu. (They will be working on the project these days.)

5. Mi smo *radili* dosta do sada. (We have been working a lot so far.)

6. On će *raditi* na projektu još neko vreme. (He will be working on the project for some more time.)